Name: Get Trolled
About the game: Hi there, this might be the hardest game you've ever played. This 2D Jump 'n' run game tries to troll you again and again until you hate it. Try to remember all the traps so you don't fall for them again. FEATURES: - 6 unique levels. - 300+ annoying hidden traps - new skins to unlock Can you beat all the levels or do you give up ? Good Luck. You're Gonna Need It :-)
